#. module: project
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:project.field_project_project__privacy_visibility
msgid ""
"Project and Task Visibility:\n"
"- Invited internal users: Can access only the project or tasks they follow. Assignees automatically get access.\n"
"- Invited internal and portal users: Same as above, extended to portal users.\n"
"- All internal users: Full access to the project and all its tasks.\n"
"- All internal and invited portal users: Internal users get full access. Portal users can access only the project or tasks they follow.\n"
"\n"
"Portal Access Levels:\n"
"- Read-only: Portal users see tasks via their portal but can’t edit them.\n"
"- Edit (limited): Portal users access kanban/list views and can edit limited fields on followed tasks.\n"
"- Edit: Same as above, with access to all tasks.\n"
"\n"
"Other Rules:\n"
"- Internal users can open a task from a direct link, even without project access.\n"
"- Project admins have access to private projects, even if not followers.\n"
msgstr ""
"Vidljivost projekta i zadataka:\n"
"- Pozvani interni korisnici: Mogu pristupiti samo projektima ili zadacima koje prate. Zaduženi automatski dobijaju pristup.\n"
"- Pozvani interni i portal korisnici: Isto kao gore, prošireno na portal korisnike.\n"
"- Svi interni korisnici: Puni pristup projektu i svim njegovim zadacima.\n"
"- Svi interni i pozvani portal korisnici: Interni korisnici imaju puni pristup. Portal korisnici mogu pristupiti samo projektima ili zadacima koje prate.\n"
"\n"
"Nivoi pristupa portalu:\n"
"- Samo čitanje: Portal korisnici vide zadatke putem portala ali ih ne mogu uređivati.\n"
"- Uređivanje (ograničeno): Portal korisnici pristupaju kanban/list pregledima i mogu uređivati ograničena polja na praćenim zadacima.\n"
"- Uređivanje: Isto kao gore, s pristupom svim zadacima.\n"
"\n"
"Ostala pravila:\n"
"- Interni korisnici mogu otvoriti zadatak putem direktnog linka, čak i bez pristupa projektu.\n"
"- Administratori projekta imaju pristup privatnim projektima, čak i ako nisu pratioci.\n"

